<i>¶ Way, hey</i>
<i>Well done, crew ¶</i>

21:42.869 --> 21:45.202
<i>¶ Everyone knew</i>
<i>just what to do ¶</i>

21:45.204 --> 21:46.937
<i>¶ Way, hey</i>
