21:46.939 --> 21:49.807
<i>¶ It's time to count</i>
<i>our gold doubloons ¶</i>

21:49.809 --> 21:52.243
Come on, count with us.

21:52.744 --> 21:54.745
[all] Yeah!

21:54.747 --> 21:58.649
[Jake]
One, two, three.

21:58.651 --> 22:00.951
[Cubby]
Four, five, six.

22:00.953 --> 22:03.120
[Izzy]
Seven, eight, nine.

22:03.122 --> 22:06.691
[Jake]
Yo-ho! For solving
pirate problems today,

22:06.693 --> 22:10.394
we got nine gold doubloons.

22:10.396 --> 22:14.498
Crackers! I never did get
to give my gift to the queen.

22:14.500 --> 22:17.668
She would have loved it.

22:17.670 --> 22:20.571
Crackers! [laughs]

22:20.573 --> 22:23.341
[all laughing]

22:26.244 --> 22:28.913
[sighs] Who'd ever thought

22:28.915 --> 22:33.417
