would get to meet royalty?

22:33.419 --> 22:36.721
[sighs]
She's ever so lovely.

22:36.723 --> 22:39.924
[sighs] Her hands
are dainty and smooth

22:39.926 --> 22:42.159
as a baby squid's bottom.

22:42.161 --> 22:45.463
Quit that mooning
and on your feet, men.

22:45.465 --> 22:47.565
- Back to work...
- [loud bang]

22:47.567 --> 22:50.801
Oh, no!

22:50.803 --> 22:54.071
A hammerhead.
[laughing]

